                <div class="tl-date">Feb 2024 — Jan 2026</div>
                <div class="tl-role">Senior Data Scientist</div>
                <div class="tl-company"><img src={`${base}raincoat-logo.png`} alt="Raincoat LLC — Climate risk technology" class="tl-logo tl-logo-sm" loading="lazy"> — Data Science Team</div>
                <ul class="tl-highlights">
                    <li>ML infrastructure for peril risk assessment</li>
                    <li>Engineered end-to-end ML pipeline</li>
