            <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
                <div class="testimonial-quote">&ldquo;I worked with St&eacute;phane at the beginning of my PhD, and I am still grateful — without his recommendations I would work and troubleshoot much less efficiently. He always takes time to explain, and never loses his sense of humor even after the nth error message.&rdquo;</div>
